steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"2jjhi","text":"For a 150bp paired-end or single-read sequencing experiment, design primers in a way that the region of interest, like CRISPR cutting site or specific mutations, locates within 130bp from at least one of the primers","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"55k12","text":"Add NGS adapters to 5’ end of primers following the instructions of your local NGS facility","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"arjh7","text":" PCR Reaction - setup","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":1,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aic85","text":"     Ultrapure H2O      10.6µl        5x HF buffer      4µl        2.5mM dNTP       1.6µl        10uM primer Forward      0.5µl        10uM primer Reverse      0.5µl        DMSO      0.6µl        Titan DNA polymerase   or Phusion      0.2µl        Crude cell lysis      2µl   ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":276}],"data":{}},{"key":"f5mef","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"tables","mutability":"","data":{"cellsMeta":{"0_0":"","0_1":"","1_0":"","1_1":"","2_0":"","2_1":"","3_0":"","3_1":"","4_0":"","4_1":"","5_0":"","5_1":"","6_0":"","6_1":"","7_0":"","7_1":""},"colTitles":["",""],"colWidths":[200,200],"data":[["  Ultrapure H2O  ","  10.6 µl  "],["  5x HF buffer  ","  4 µl  "],["  2.5 mM dNTP   ","  1.6 µl  "],["  10 µM primer Forward  ","  0.5 µl  "],["  10 µM primer Reverse  ","  0.5 µl  "],["  DMSO  ","  0.6 µl  "],["  Titan DNA polymerase\n  or Phusion  ","  0.2 µl  "],["  Crude cell lysate  ","  2 µl  "]],"guid":"441EE9687CDB11EC897E0A58A9FEAC02","isJexcelDataFormat":true,"legend":"","mergeCells":{},"printData":[["  Ultrapure H2O  ","  10.6 µl  "],["  5x HF buffer  ","  4 µl  "],["  2.5 mM dNTP   ","  1.6 µl  "],["  10 µM primer Forward  ","  0.5 µl  "],["  10 µM primer Reverse  ","  0.5 µl  "],["  DMSO  ","  0.6 µl  "],["  Titan DNA polymerase\n  or Phusion  ","  0.2 µl  "],["  Crude cell lysate  ","  2 µl  "]],"rowHeights":[23,23,23,23,23,23,23,23]}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5a28a","text":"Calculate the amount of each component needed for all samples, also count a negative control and positive control","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9b3a","text":"In a pre-PCR area, mix all components except the crude cell lysate to a microcentrifuge tube or a 15 ml conical tube to make master mix","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3u0e4","text":"Aliquot 18 µl to each 200 µl microcentrifuge tube or each well in a 96-well PCR plate. Use reservoir and multi-channel pipet if there are many samples.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"enn0i","text":"Add 2 µl crude cell lysate to the reaction. In one reaction, use 2 µl H2O instead as negative control. In another reaction, use 2 µl previously validated crude cell lysate as positive control.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"5rav7","text":"Cap the tubes or seal the plates properly with an adhesive seal.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"7ucia","text":"Shake the tubes or plates vigorously to mix","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"88q8a","text":"Use the following touch-down PCR protocol in a thermocycler","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"a89q2","text":" Touch-down PCR protocol","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":24}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"q5b5","text":"     98C      3min        98C      30s        70C (touch down,   1C/cycle)      30s        72C      30s        Go to 2       12 cycles in total        98C      30s        58C      30s        72C      30s        Go to 6       23 cycles in total        72C      7min        4C or 12C      forever   ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":297}],"data":{}},{"key":"at0bg","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"tables","mutability":"","data":{"cellsMeta":{"0_0":"","0_1":"","10_0":"","10_1":"","1_0":"","1_1":"","2_0":"","2_1":"","3_0":"","3_1":"","4_0":"","4_1":"","5_0":"","5_1":"","6_0":"","6_1":"","7_0":"","7_1":"","8_0":"","8_1":"","9_0":"","9_1":""},"colTitles":["",""],"colWidths":[145,144],"data":[["  98°C  ","  3min  "],["  98°C  ","  30s  "],["  70°C (touch down,\n  1°C/cycle)  ","  30s  "],["  72°C  ","  30s  "],["  Go to 2   ","  12 cycles in total  "],["  98°C  ","  30s  "],["  58°C  ","  30s  "],["  72°C  ","  30s  "],["  Go to 6   ","  23 cycles in total  "],["  72°C  ","  7min  "],["  4°C or 12°C  ","  forever  "]],"guid":"B8AE6E2F7CDB11EC897E0A58A9FEAC02","isJexcelDataFormat":true,"legend":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"28qpk","text":"","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}},"mergeCells":{},"printData":[["  98°C  ","  3min  "],["  98°C  ","  30s  "],["  70°C (touch down,\n  1°C/cycle)  ","  30s  "],["  72°C  ","  30s  "],["  Go to 2   ","  12 cycles in total  "],["  98°C  ","  30s  "],["  58°C  ","  30s  "],["  72°C  ","  30s  "],["  Go to 6   ","  23 cycles in total  "],["  72°C  ","  7min  "],["  4°C or 12°C  ","  forever  "]],"rowHeights":[23,23,23,23,23,23,23,23,23,23,23]}}}}
